| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2712 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: afb3b0c4-73a4-58b4-adad-a71f1afda4ee"
